304
00:25:50,674 --> 00:25:52,918
Dan kamu ada di sampingku,
benar-benar sia-sia,

305
00:25:52,918 --> 00:25:55,138
memesan pertukaran driver,

306
00:25:55,138 --> 00:25:59,268
